Emacs Lisp port of Dark Souls. Prepare to die.

Dark Souls is now available on [MELPA](http://melpa.milkbox.net/)!
```
M-x package-install dark-souls
```

To start playing in the current buffer:

```
M-x dark-souls-mode
```

